text: Laura Freigang (born 1 February 1998) is a German footballer who plays as a forward for Eintracht Frankfurt and the Germany national team. ==Career== Freigang made her international debut for Germany on 7 March 2020 in the 2020 Algarve Cup against Norway, which finished as a 4–0 win. ==Career statistics== ===International=== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- !colspan=3|Germany |- !Year!!Apps!!Goals |- |2020||2||0 |- !Total!!2!!0 |} ===International goals=== Scores and results list Germany's goal tally first: {| class="wikitable" |- !colspan="7"|Leupolz – goals for Germany |- ! # !!
